The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, roller, ship, trike
 1. the french is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 2. the person traveling to nizza is the person eating cabbage##1
 3. the person eating banana is not the turkish##6
 4. the person eating cabbage is not the person traveling to hamburg##6
 5. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
 7. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
 8. the person traveling to rome is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 9. the person driving the roller is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the trike##7
10. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
11. the turkish is the person traveling to rome##1
12. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere between the person traveling to rome and the person eating spinach##7
13. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the brazilian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3     |    4     |
