 3. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
 4. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
 5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
 6. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 7. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the right of the cain-smoker##5
 8. the person driving the ship is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person eating eggplant and the person eating tomato##7
10. the blend-smoker is in an even position##4
11. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
12. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
13. the ritmeester-smoker is not the person driving the scooter##6
14. the cain-smoker is not the person eating onion##6
