.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, cooking, puzzles, sudoku
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, blue, coral, turquise
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, colombian, french, malaysian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, rowing, skateboarding, soccer
 1. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the brazilian is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5
 4. the french is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the french##5
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is rowing##7
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
10. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the french##1
11. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Hobby         | chess      | cooking   | sudoku   | puzzles       |
| Color   | turquise | lilac    | blue | coral       |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | colombian | french   | malaysian     |
| Sport         | baseball   | soccer    | rowing   | skateboarding |

