.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, mirinda, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, snowboarding, golf, cycling
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, hiking, reading
4 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, hamster, rabbit
 1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the hamster##2
 4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the owner of the goldfish##6
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
 7. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's sport is cycling##7
 8. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
 9. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is golf##1
12. the person who's sport is golf is not the owner of the hamster##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk   | tea     | mirinda   | iced-tea |
| Sport       | cycling   | basketball | snowboarding | golf    |
| Hobby      | hiking | reading | dancing   | drawing  |
| Pet        | rabbit | cat     | hamster   | goldfish |

