.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, hiking, singing
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, fisherman, musician, videographer
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit, snake
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, polish, colombian, german
 1. the german is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
 2. the musician is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 3. the polish is the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
 5. the architect is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the musician and the person who's hobby is baking##7
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is the australian##1
 9. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
10. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
11. the colombian is in an even position##4
12. the architect is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby   | singing      | hiking     | cooking   | baking    |
| Job     | videographer | musician   | fisherman | architect |
| Pet     | snake        | rabbit     | goldfish  | pony      |
| Nationality   | polish       | german | australian   | colombian    |

 